{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Character encoding（字符编码）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/character_encoding","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>一套编码系统定义字节与文本间的映射。一连串字节文本能让不同文本解释得以进行。我们指明一套特定编码系统时（如 UTF-8），也就指明了字节得以解释的方式。</p>\n<p>例如，我们通常在 HTML 里声明 UTF-8 字符编码，使用如下：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>这就确保你在 HTML 文档中可以使用几乎任何一种人类语言中的字符，并且会稳定显示。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常识","title":"常识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/definitions-characters/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Character encoding on W3C</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Character_encoding\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Character encoding</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"一套编码系统定义字节与文本间的映射。一连串字节文本能让不同文本解释得以进行。我们指明一套特定编码系统时（如 UTF-8），也就指明了字节得以解释的方式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Character encoding","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Codificación de caracteres","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Codage des caractères","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Character encoding (文字エンコーディング)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Character encoding","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Character enc